7334,"updated_time":1545877334,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看你们那么多高赞回答，都是在嘲讽提问者\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们说，就算他“证明”出来，“肯定”是用了很多所谓的“常识”来证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e荒诞的是，你们这种嘲笑的行为，本身就是将“中学生不能证明哥德巴赫猜想”作为了“常识”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他最后能否证明出来都还未可知，但已经引起你们的群嘲，莫非你们心里面是渴望被“打脸”？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560533737,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ee9b015adabdbc4790840e1a8b5cc5cc","url_token":"huang-peng-fei-36-40","name":"黄大九","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f0bc833c8c00f581084d474110474580_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f0bc833c8c00f581084d474110474580_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ee9b015adabdbc4790840e1a8b5cc5cc","user_type":"people","headline":"你懂的越少，懂你的越多","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560533737","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545851395,"updated_time":1545851395,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e那个东西 我十年前就证出来了那么大一堆擦屁股嫌硬的纸 现在还放在床底下吃灰呢 \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561011124,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"htt